verely ill.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/117152/', '', 'Tinidazole, Pantoprazole, Dexlansoprazole, Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Metronidazole, Famotidine, Rifabutin, Cimetidine, Esomeprazole, More', '', 1767369485);
