verely ill.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/117157/', '', 'Rifamycin, Kanamycin, Ampicillin, Azithromycin, Acyclovir, Netilmicin, Polymyxin B, Famciclovir, Cefuroxime, Trifluridine, Benzylpenicillin, More', '', 1767369485);
